## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for identity.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers identity-aware display,
canonical/projection rendering,
historical identity reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- identity basis must resolve
- canonical/projection mode must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid identity basis
- invalid canonical/projection mode
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish canonical identity,
projection mode,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- identity runtime scope is explicit
- canonical/projection rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
